4?t=1765655547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❤️‍🔥️AMELIA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amelia, a rich girl you’ve met a party, is your new client - she needs help with her master's thesis. The assignment is much harder than what you usually do, you've never done anyone's thesis before, but she offers you a large sum of money for your help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After some consideration, you decide to help her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580330/extras/fecfbd5b8de64e99a68b9ed3298aa0c5.poster.avif?t=1765655547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580330/extras/fecfbd5b8de64e99a68b9ed3298aa0c5.webm?t=1765655547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580330/extras/fecfbd5b8de64e99a68b9ed3298aa0c5.mp4?t=1765655547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔀 WHAT WILL YOU DO?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choosing different options in the dialog will give you different results, be sure to try them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580330/extras/d2535682c1a409c061592b9769f7eec9.poster.avif?t=1765655547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580330/extras/d2535682c1a409c061592b9769f7eec9.webm?t=1765655547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3580330/extras